results.name: Values of k corresponding to A073726.
comment: If there is more than one choice for k then the smallest value is taken.
link: A. J. Menezes, P. C. van Oorschot and S. A. Vanstone, Handbook of Applied Cryptography, CRC Press, 1996; see Table 4.8.
mathematica: f[n_] := For[k = 1, k <= n - 1, k++, If[PrimitivePolynomialQ[x^n + x^k + 1, 2], Print[k]; Return[k]]];
